### Examples

Using the same Spark session and models created in the previous section
we start by loading `broom`:


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(broom)
```
:::


To view the estimates for each term simply pass `mtcars_model` to the
`tidy()` function:




::: {.cell warnings='false'}

